	(103, 2, '<b>Rigatoni Pasta Sauce Nugget "S"</b>', 'rigatoni-pasta-sauce-nugget-s.html', '<b>Rigatoni Pasta Sauce Nugget "S"</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>470 gr </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET "S"</a></strong></span></li><li><span>1 tbsp margarin</span></li><li><span>1 pcs bawang bombay,finely chopped</span></li><li><span>2 cloves garlic,memarkan</span></li><li><span>1 tsp italian seasoning</span></li><li><span>4 tbsp saus sambal</span></li><li><span>2 tbsp saus tomat</span></li><li><span>½ pcs paprika merah, thinly sliced</span></li><li><span>½ pcs paprika hijau, thinly sliced</span></li><li><span>Garam, sugar, and ground pepper to taste</span></li><li><span>200 gr pasta rigatoni, rebuslalu tiriskan</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Heat margarin, lalu saute bawang bombay, garlic, and italian seasoning until fragrant.&nbsp;Add saus sambal and saus tomat, aduk rata.</span></li><li><span>Add merica, garam, sugar, and paprika, aduk hingga matang.&nbsp;Angkat.</span></li><li><span>Susun pasta that sudah direbus di atas piring saji,lalu tuang with saus and taburi with <strong>ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET "S"</strong>.</span></li><li><span>Serve with taburan grated cheese.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-NuggetS-Pasta.jpg', '', '', 1, 7, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:27:58', '2026-03-16 16:27:58'),
	(104, 2, '<b>Nasi Kuning Gulung Isi Nugget Stick</b>', 'nasi-kuning-gulung-isi-nugget-stick.html', '<b>Nasi Kuning Gulung Isi Nugget Stick</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>470 gr </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET STICK</a></span></strong></li><li><span>100 gr beras ketan, rendam</span></li><li><span>100 gr beras</span></li><li><span>250 ml santan cair</span></li><li><span>3 cm kunyit, haluskan</span></li><li><span>3 sheets daun jeruk</span></li><li><span>Salt to taste</span></li><li><span>5 sheets thin omelet sheets</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Campur beras ketan, beras,santan cair, kunyit, daun jeruk, and garam, masak hingga become aron lalu kukus hingga matang.</span></li><li><span>Ambil sesheets dadar telur lalu beri yellow rice, ratakan. Add <strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET STICK</a></span></strong> goreng di tengahnya.</span></li><li><span>Gulung hingga padat and rapi, potong-potong and sajikan.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-NasiKuning.jpg', '', '', 1, 6, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:28:01', '2026-03-16 16:28:01'),
	(105, 2, '<b>Cordon Bleu With Tomato Sauce</b>', 'cordon-bleu-with-tomato-sauce.html', '<b>Cordon Bleu With Tomato Sauce</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>250 gr </span><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span></li><li><span>Cooking oil as needed</span></li><li><span>200 gr spageti, rebus matang</span></li><li><span>1 tbsp peterseli chopped<br><br>Tomato Sauce:<br></span></li><li><span>2 tbsp margarin</span></li><li><span>½ pcs bawang bombay,finely chopped</span></li><li><span>1 cloves garlic, finely chopped</span></li><li><span>2 pcs tomat, diced</span></li><li><span>5 tbsp saus tomat</span></li><li><span>2 tbsp saus sambal</span></li><li><span>Garam, sugar, and merica </span><span>bubuk secukupnya</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Heat minyak, goreng <span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span> hingga matang. Remove and drain.</span></li><li><span>Saus tomat: Heat margarin, saute bawang bombay and garlic until fragrant. Add tomat, saus tomat, saus sambal, garam, sugar, and ground pepper. Cook until matang, angkat.</span></li><li><span> Susun spageti and <span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span> dalam piring saji, lalu tuang saus tomat di atasnya. Taburi with peterseli chopped, sajikan.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-CordonBleu-Tomato1.jpg', '', '', 1, 8, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:28:01', '2026-03-16 16:28:01'),
